item.title: CVE-2023-5960|2024-08-02T08:14:25.225Z -- zyxel -- usg%20flex%20series%20firmware
item.description: An improper privilege management vulnerability in the hotspot feature of the Zyxel USG FLEX series firmware versions 4.50 through 5.37 and VPN series firmware versions 4.30 through 5.37 could allow an authenticated local attacker to access the system files on an affected device.
